      "span_text": "Previously, 60 of the 186 tested individuals had also been typed for 30 single-nucleotide polymorphisms (SNPs) dispersed along a 2.4 Mb region encompassing G6PD and including rs1573656, a silent marker SNP in OPN1LW [CITATION_1] ."
